Installation Required:

Below are the steps required to configure project in local system

pip install virtualenv
virtualenv <env>
cd <env>
for Linux: run source bin/activate
for windows: run Scripts/activate.bat

pip install --upgrade pip

git clone https://github.com/sivachandranp/recruitsite.git

cd recruitsite/jobportal

pip install -r requirements.txt

Modification Required:

1. To configure local database update database name, username & password in settings.py
2. To create model, run
  2.1 python manage.py makemigrations
  2.2 python manage.py migrate
3. To setup an admin account run 
  3.1 python manage.py createsuperuser
4. To run development server, enter the below command
    python manage.py runserver
5. To goto admin portal type url http:<servername>:<port>/admin in address bar 

